  <h3>Haali Reader - a book reader for Windows CE</h3>
  <p>After I tried a few existing apps I still couldnt find anything that had
  all required features and was easy to use. The main problem was the lack of
  support for cyrillic encodings. So I decided to write my own bookreader.
  </p>
  <p>Some (scarce) <a href="docs.html.en">documentation</a>, thanks to Chris Clark for providing a skeleton</p>
